language Essence 1.3

given n_middle: int(1..100)
given n_delta: int(0..49)
find n: int(1..100)
such that
    n >= n_middle - n_delta,
    n <= n_middle + n_delta
given k_middle: int(1..100)
given k_delta: int(0..49)
find k: int(1..100)
such that
    k >= k_middle - k_delta,
    k <= k_middle + k_delta
such that k < sum([i | i : int(1..100), i <= n])
